      <span class="section-tag">📚 PILLAR GUIDES</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Complete Guides</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Comprehensive, in-depth guides covering entire topics.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tools-grid">
      <a class="tool-card" href="/sites/28grams/essential-spices-guide">
        <span class="tool-emoji">🌶️</span>
        <h3 class="tool-name">Essential Spices Guide</h3>
        <p class="tool-desc">The 30 most essential spices for any kitchen.</p>
